snippet.textDisplay:
I love this song and I am listening to it every day too... I am French and I love listening to Punjabi language. Yes the subtitles are very useful... I don't live in the same kind of society...and I am happy that a man can date me without wanting to marry me ! But everywhere in the world, traditions are disappearing... and everybody wonders where this mad world is going...and I like very much the conclusion in this song...Only God knows...
 I don't know at all these 2 singers...but they both have very beautiful voices...very close voices actually. And though they don't belong to the same generation and are not dressed the same at all, they look so happy singing this song together. I don't know why, the lyrics about the rivers always move me...Poetic image...Nature is one, as Music is...No boundaries...Thanks a lot Gurdas Maan and Diljit Dosanjh for this song... Would you believe this song is loved in France ???
